      <title>特朗普恐慌后哥伦比亚意外停止关键利率下调</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/colombia-unexpectedly-halts-interest-rate-cuts-amid-fiscal-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于政策制定者担心财政前景恶化、最低工资大幅上调以及美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的关税威胁，哥伦比亚意外停止了从 2023 年开始的一系列降息举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/colombia-unexpectedly-halts-interest-rate-cuts-amid-fiscal-fears</guid>
