    <item>
      <title>报道称特朗普将推迟征收关税，加元和墨西哥比索飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/dollar-falls-on-report-that-us-tariffs-delayed-until-march-1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有报道称特朗普总统将推迟实施关税，加拿大和墨西哥货币因此上涨，在经历了连续下跌之后，为两国货币带来一些缓解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/dollar-falls-on-report-that-us-tariffs-delayed-until-march-1</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 17:47:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合利华考虑将纽约作为冰淇淋业务上市地点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/unilever-weighs-us-as-potential-listing-venue-for-ice-cream-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，联合利华公司正在考虑将纽约作为其冰淇淋业务上市的潜在地点，此举可能会引发该部门本土市场荷兰的强烈反对。]]></description>
